var book = {
	"name": "Hosea",
	"numChapters": 14,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> which came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22096A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22096A\"></sup>Hosea the son of Beeri, during the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22096B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22096B\"></sup>Uzziah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22096C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22096C\"></sup>Jotham, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22096D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22096D\"></sup>Ahaz <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22096E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22096E\"></sup>Hezekiah, kings of Judah, and during the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22096F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22096F\"></sup>Jeroboam the son of Joash, king of Israel.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> first spoke through Hosea, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Hosea, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22097G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22097G\"></sup>Go, take to yourself a wife of harlotry and <i>have</i> children of harlotry; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22097H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22097H\"></sup>the land commits flagrant harlotry, forsaking the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So he went and took Gomer the daughter of Diblaim, and she conceived and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22098I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22098I\"></sup>bore him a son.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to him, “Name him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22099J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22099J\"></sup>Jezreel; for yet a little while, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22099K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22099K\"></sup>I will punish the house of Jehu for the bloodshed of Jezreel, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22099L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22099L\"></sup>I will put an end to the kingdom of the house of Israel.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>On that day I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22100M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22100M\"></sup>break the bow of Israel in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22100N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22100N\"></sup>valley of Jezreel.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then she conceived again and gave birth to a daughter. And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to him, “Name her Lo-ruhamah, for I will no longer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22101O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22101O\"></sup>have compassion on the house of Israel, that I would ever forgive them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But I will have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22102P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22102P\"></sup>compassion on the house of Judah and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22102Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22102Q\"></sup>deliver them by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God, and will not deliver them by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22102R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22102R\"></sup>bow, sword, battle, horses or horsemen.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When she had weaned Lo-ruhamah, she conceived and gave birth to a son.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “Name him Lo-ammi, for you are not My people and I am not your God.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Yet the number of the sons of IsraelWill be like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22105S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22105S\"></sup>sand of the sea,Which cannot be measured or numbered;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22105T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22105T\"></sup>in the placeWhere it is said to them,“You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22105U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22105U\"></sup>not My people,”It will be said to them,“<i>You are</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22105V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22105V\"></sup>sons of the living God.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22106W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22106W\"></sup>sons of Judah and the sons of Israel will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22106X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22106X\"></sup>gathered together,And they will appoint for themselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22106Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22106Y\"></sup>one leader,And they will go up from the land,For great will be the day of Jezreel."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Say to your brothers, “Ammi,” and to your sisters, “Ruhamah.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Contend with your mother, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22108A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22108A\"></sup>contend,For she is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22108B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22108B\"></sup>not my wife, and I am not her husband;And let her put away her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22108C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22108C\"></sup>harlotry from her faceAnd her adultery from between her breasts,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Or I will strip her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22109D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22109D\"></sup>nakedAnd expose her as on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22109E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22109E\"></sup>day when she was born.I will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22109F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22109F\"></sup>make her like a wilderness,Make her like desert landAnd slay her with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22109G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22109G\"></sup>thirst.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Also, I will have no compassion on her children,Because they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22110H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22110H\"></sup>children of harlotry.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“For their mother has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22111I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22111I\"></sup>played the harlot;She who conceived them has acted shamefully.For she said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22111J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22111J\"></sup>I will go after my lovers,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22111K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22111K\"></sup>give <i>me</i> my bread and my water,My wool and my flax, my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22111L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22111L\"></sup>oil and my drink.’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Therefore, behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22112M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22112M\"></sup>hedge up her way with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22112N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22112N\"></sup>thorns,And I will build a wall against her so that she cannot find her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22112O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22112O\"></sup>paths.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“She will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22113P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22113P\"></sup>pursue her lovers, but she will not overtake them;And she will seek them, but will not find <i>them</i>.Then she will say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22113Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22113Q\"></sup>I will go back to my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22113R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22113R\"></sup>first husband,For it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22113S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22113S\"></sup>better for me then than now!’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“For she does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22114T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22114T\"></sup>not know that it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22114U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22114U\"></sup>I who gave her the grain, the new wine and the oil,And lavished on her silver and gold,<i>Which</i> they used for Baal.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Therefore, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22115V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22115V\"></sup>take back My grain at harvest timeAnd My new wine in its season.I will also take away My wool and My flax<i>Given</i> to cover her nakedness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“And then I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22116W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22116W\"></sup>uncover her lewdnessIn the sight of her lovers,And no one will rescue her out of My hand.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“I will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22117X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22117X\"></sup>put an end to all her gaiety,Her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22117Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22117Y\"></sup>feasts, her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22117Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22117Z\"></sup>new moons, her sabbathsAnd all her festal assemblies.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22118AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22118AA\"></sup>destroy her vines and fig trees,Of which she said, ‘These are my wagesWhich my lovers have given me.’And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22118AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22118AB\"></sup>make them a forest,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22118AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22118AC\"></sup>beasts of the field will devour them.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“I will punish her for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22119AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22119AD\"></sup>days of the BaalsWhen she used to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22119AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22119AE\"></sup>offer sacrifices to themAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22119AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22119AF\"></sup>adorn herself with her earrings and jewelry,And follow her lovers, so that she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22119AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22119AG\"></sup>forgot Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Therefore, behold, I will allure her,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22120AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22120AH\"></sup>Bring her into the wildernessAnd speak kindly to her.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Then I will give her her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22121AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22121AI\"></sup>vineyards from there,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22121AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22121AJ\"></sup>the valley of Achor as a door of hope.And she will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22121AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22121AK\"></sup>sing there as in the days of her youth,As in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22121AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22121AL\"></sup>day when she came up from the land of Egypt.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“It will come about in that day,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“That you will call Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22122AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22122AM\"></sup>IshiAnd will no longer call Me Baali.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22123AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22123AN\"></sup>I will remove the names of the Baals from her mouth,So that they will be mentioned by their names no more.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“In that day I will also make a covenant for themWith the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22124AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22124AO\"></sup>beasts of the field,The birds of the skyAnd the creeping things of the ground.And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22124AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22124AP\"></sup>abolish the bow, the sword and war from the land,And will make them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22124AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22124AQ\"></sup>lie down in safety.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22125AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22125AR\"></sup>betroth you to Me forever;Yes, I will betroth you to Me in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22125AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22125AS\"></sup>righteousness and in justice,In lovingkindness and in compassion,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And I will betroth you to Me in faithfulness.Then you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22126AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22126AT\"></sup>know the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“It will come about in that day that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22127AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22127AU\"></sup>I will respond,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“I will respond to the heavens, and they will respond to the earth,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22128AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22128AV\"></sup>earth will respond to the grain, to the new wine and to the oil,And they will respond to Jezreel.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22129AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22129AW\"></sup>sow her for Myself in the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22129AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22129AX\"></sup>I will also have compassion on her who had not obtained compassion,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22129AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22129AY\"></sup>I will say to those who were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22129AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22129AZ\"></sup>not My people,‘You are My people!’And they will say, ‘<i>You are</i> my God!’”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Go again, love a woman <i>who</i> is loved by <i>her</i> husband, yet an adulteress, even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22130A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22130A\"></sup>as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> loves the sons of Israel, though they turn to other gods and love raisin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22130B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22130B\"></sup>cakes.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22131C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22131C\"></sup>bought her for myself for fifteen <i>shekels</i> of silver and a homer and a half of barley.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then I said to her, “You shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22132D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22132D\"></sup>stay with me for many days. You shall not play the harlot, nor shall you have a man; so I will also be toward you.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For the sons of Israel will remain for many days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22133E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22133E\"></sup>without king or prince, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22133F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22133F\"></sup>without sacrifice or <i>sacred</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22133G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22133G\"></sup>pillar and without <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22133H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22133H\"></sup>ephod or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22133I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22133I\"></sup>household idols.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Afterward the sons of Israel will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22134J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22134J\"></sup>return and seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22134K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22134K\"></sup>David their king; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22134L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22134L\"></sup>they will come trembling to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and to His goodness in the last days."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22135A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22135A\"></sup>Listen to the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O sons of Israel,For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22135B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22135B\"></sup>case against the inhabitants of the land,Because there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22135C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22135C\"></sup>no faithfulness or kindnessOr <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22135D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22135D\"></sup>knowledge of God in the land.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><i>There is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22136E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22136E\"></sup>swearing, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22136F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22136F\"></sup>deception, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22136G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22136G\"></sup>murder, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22136H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22136H\"></sup>stealing and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22136I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22136I\"></sup>adultery.They employ violence, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22136J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22136J\"></sup>bloodshed follows bloodshed.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore the land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22137K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22137K\"></sup>mourns,And everyone who lives in it languishesAlong with the beasts of the field and the birds of the sky,And also the fish of the sea disappear.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Yet let no one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22138L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22138L\"></sup>find fault, and let none offer reproof;For your people are like those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22138M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22138M\"></sup>contend with the priest.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22139N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22139N\"></sup>stumble by day,And the prophet also will stumble with you by night;And I will destroy your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22139O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22139O\"></sup>mother.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22140P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22140P\"></sup>My people are destroyed for lack of knowledge.Because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22140Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22140Q\"></sup>rejected knowledge,I also will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22140R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22140R\"></sup>reject you from being My priest.Since you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22140S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22140S\"></sup>forgotten the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22140T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22140T\"></sup>law of your God,I also will forget your children.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The more they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22141U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22141U\"></sup>multiplied, the more they sinned against Me;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22141V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22141V\"></sup>change their glory into shame.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22142W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22142W\"></sup>feed on the sin of My peopleAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22142X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22142X\"></sup>direct their desire toward their iniquity.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And it will be, like people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22143Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22143Y\"></sup>like priest;So I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22143Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22143Z\"></sup>punish them for their waysAnd repay them for their deeds.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22144AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22144AA\"></sup>They will eat, but not have enough;They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22144AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22144AB\"></sup>play the harlot, but not increase,Because they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22144AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22144AC\"></sup>stopped giving heed to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Harlotry, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22145AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22145AD\"></sup>wine and new wine take away the understanding.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>My people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22146AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22146AE\"></sup>consult their wooden idol, and their <i>diviner’s</i> wand informs them;For a spirit of harlotry has led <i>them</i> astray,And they have played the harlot, <i>departing</i> from their God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>They offer sacrifices on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22147AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22147AF\"></sup>tops of the mountainsAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22147AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22147AG\"></sup>burn incense on the hills,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22147AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22147AH\"></sup>Under oak, poplar and terebinth,Because their shade is pleasant.Therefore your daughters play the harlotAnd your brides commit adultery.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will not punish your daughters when they play the harlotOr your brides when they commit adultery,For <i>the men</i> themselves go apart with harlotsAnd offer sacrifices with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22148AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22148AI\"></sup>temple prostitutes;So the people without understanding are ruined.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Though you, Israel, play the harlot,Do not let Judah become guilty;Also do not go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22149AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22149AJ\"></sup>Gilgal,Or go up to Beth-aven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22149AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22149AK\"></sup>And take the oath:“As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives!”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Since Israel is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22150AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22150AL\"></sup>stubbornLike a stubborn heifer,Can the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22150AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22150AM\"></sup>pasture themLike a lamb in a large field?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Ephraim is joined to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22151AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22151AN\"></sup>idols;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22151AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22151AO\"></sup>Let him alone.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Their liquor gone,They play the harlot continually;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22152AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22152AP\"></sup>Their rulers dearly love shame.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22153AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22153AQ\"></sup>The wind wraps them in its wings,And they will be ashamed because of their sacrifices."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Hear this, O priests!Give heed, O house of Israel!Listen, O house of the king!For the judgment applies to you,For you have been a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22154A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22154A\"></sup>snare at MizpahAnd a net spread out on Tabor.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22155B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22155B\"></sup>revolters have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22155C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22155C\"></sup>gone deep in depravity,But I will chastise all of them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22156D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22156D\"></sup>know Ephraim, and Israel is not hidden from Me;For now, O Ephraim, you have played the harlot,Israel has defiled itself.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Their deeds will not allow themTo return to their God.For a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22157E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22157E\"></sup>spirit of harlotry is within them,And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22157F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22157F\"></sup>do not know the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Moreover, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22158G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22158G\"></sup>pride of Israel testifies against him,And Israel and Ephraim stumble in their iniquity;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22158H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22158H\"></sup>Judah also has stumbled with them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22159I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22159I\"></sup>go with their flocks and herdsTo seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, but they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22159J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22159J\"></sup>not find <i>Him</i>;He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22159K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22159K\"></sup>withdrawn from them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22160L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22160L\"></sup>dealt treacherously against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,For they have borne <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22160M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22160M\"></sup>illegitimate children.Now the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22160N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22160N\"></sup>new moon will devour them with their land.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22161O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22161O\"></sup>Blow the horn in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22161P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22161P\"></sup>Gibeah,The trumpet in Ramah.Sound an alarm at Beth-aven:“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22161Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22161Q\"></sup>Behind you, Benjamin!”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Ephraim will become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22162R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22162R\"></sup>desolation in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22162S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22162S\"></sup>day of rebuke;Among the tribes of Israel I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22162T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22162T\"></sup>declare what is sure.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The princes of Judah have become like those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22163U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22163U\"></sup>move a boundary;On them I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22163V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22163V\"></sup>pour out My wrath <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22163W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22163W\"></sup>like water.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Ephraim is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22164X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22164X\"></sup>oppressed, crushed in judgment,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22164Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22164Y\"></sup>Because he was determined to follow <i>man’s</i> command.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore I am like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22165Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22165Z\"></sup>moth to EphraimAnd like rottenness to the house of Judah.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When Ephraim saw his sickness,And Judah his wound,Then Ephraim went to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22166AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22166AA\"></sup>AssyriaAnd sent to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22166AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22166AB\"></sup>King Jareb.But he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22166AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22166AC\"></sup>unable to heal you,Or to cure you of your wound.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For I <i>will be</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22167AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22167AD\"></sup>like a lion to EphraimAnd like a young lion to the house of Judah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22167AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22167AE\"></sup>I, even I, will tear to pieces and go away,I will carry away, and there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22167AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22167AF\"></sup>none to deliver.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I will go away <i>and</i> return to My placeUntil they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22168AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22168AG\"></sup>acknowledge their guilt and seek My face;In their affliction they will earnestly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22168AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22168AH\"></sup>seek Me."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22169A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22169A\"></sup>Come, let us return to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22169B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22169B\"></sup>He has torn <i>us</i>, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22169C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22169C\"></sup>He will heal us;He has wounded <i>us</i>, but He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22169D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22169D\"></sup>bandage us.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22170E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22170E\"></sup>revive us after two days;He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22170F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22170F\"></sup>raise us up on the third day,That we may live before Him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“So let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22171G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22171G\"></sup>know, let us press on to know the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22171H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22171H\"></sup>going forth is as certain as the dawn;And He will come to us like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22171I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22171I\"></sup>rain,Like the spring rain watering the earth.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>What shall I do with you, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22172J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22172J\"></sup>Ephraim?What shall I do with you, O Judah?For your loyalty is like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22172K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22172K\"></sup>morning cloudAnd like the dew which goes away early.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Therefore I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22173L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22173L\"></sup>hewn <i>them</i> in pieces by the prophets;I have slain them by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22173M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22173M\"></sup>words of My mouth;And the judgments on you are <i>like</i> the light that goes forth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22174N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22174N\"></sup>I delight in loyalty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22174O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22174O\"></sup>rather than sacrifice,And in the knowledge of God rather than burnt offerings.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22175P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22175P\"></sup>like Adam they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22175Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22175Q\"></sup>transgressed the covenant;There they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22175R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22175R\"></sup>dealt treacherously against Me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22176S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22176S\"></sup>Gilead is a city of wrongdoers,Tracked with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22176T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22176T\"></sup>bloody <i>footprints</i>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22177U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22177U\"></sup>raiders wait for a man,<i>So</i> a band of priests <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22177V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22177V\"></sup>murder on the way to Shechem;Surely they have committed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22177W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22177W\"></sup>crime.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In the house of Israel I have seen a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22178X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22178X\"></sup>horrible thing;Ephraim’s <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22178Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22178Y\"></sup>harlotry is there, Israel has defiled itself.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Also, O Judah, there is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22179Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22179Z\"></sup>harvest appointed for you,When I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22179AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22179AA\"></sup>restore the fortunes of My people."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>When I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22180A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22180A\"></sup>would heal Israel,The iniquity of Ephraim is uncovered,And the evil deeds of Samaria,For they deal <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22180B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22180B\"></sup>falsely;The thief enters in,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22180C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22180C\"></sup>Bandits raid outside,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And they do not consider in their heartsThat I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22181D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22181D\"></sup>remember all their wickedness.Now their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22181E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22181E\"></sup>deeds are all around them;They are before My face.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22182F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22182F\"></sup>With their wickedness they make the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22182G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22182G\"></sup>king glad,And the princes with their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22182H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22182H\"></sup>lies.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22183I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22183I\"></sup>all adulterers,Like an oven heated by the bakerWho ceases to stir up <i>the fire</i>From the kneading of the dough until it is leavened.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>On the day of our king, the princes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22184J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22184J\"></sup>became sick with the heat of wine;He stretched out his hand with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22184K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22184K\"></sup>scoffers,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For their hearts are like an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22185L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22185L\"></sup>oven<i>As</i> they approach their plotting;Their anger smolders all night,In the morning it burns like a flaming fire.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>All of them are hot like an oven,And they consume their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22186M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22186M\"></sup>rulers;All their kings have fallen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22186N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22186N\"></sup>None of them calls on Me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Ephraim <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22187O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22187O\"></sup>mixes himself with the nations;Ephraim has become a cake not turned.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22188P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22188P\"></sup>Strangers devour his strength,Yet he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22188Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22188Q\"></sup>does not know <i>it</i>;Gray hairs also are sprinkled on him,Yet he does not know <i>it</i>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Though the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22189R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22189R\"></sup>pride of Israel testifies against him,Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22189S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22189S\"></sup>they have not returned to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God,Nor have they sought Him, for all this.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22190T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22190T\"></sup>Ephraim has become like a silly dove, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22190U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22190U\"></sup>without sense;They call to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22190V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22190V\"></sup>Egypt, they go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22190W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22190W\"></sup>Assyria.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When they go, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22191X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22191X\"></sup>spread My net over them;I will bring them down like the birds of the sky.I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22191Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22191Y\"></sup>chastise them in accordance with the proclamation to their assembly.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22192Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22192Z\"></sup>Woe to them, for they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22192AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22192AA\"></sup>strayed from Me!Destruction is theirs, for they have rebelled against Me!I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22192AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22192AB\"></sup>would redeem them, but they speak lies against Me.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22193AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22193AC\"></sup>they do not cry to Me from their heartWhen they wail on their beds;For the sake of grain and new wine they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22193AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22193AD\"></sup>assemble themselves,They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22193AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22193AE\"></sup>turn away from Me.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Although I trained <i>and</i> strengthened their arms,Yet they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22194AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22194AF\"></sup>devise evil against Me.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>They turn, <i>but</i> not upward,They are like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22195AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22195AG\"></sup>deceitful bow;Their princes will fall by the swordBecause of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22195AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22195AH\"></sup>insolence of their tongue.This <i>will be</i> their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22195AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22195AI\"></sup>derision in the land of Egypt."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22196A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22196A\"></sup><i>Put</i> the trumpet to your lips!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22196B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22196B\"></sup>Like an eagle <i>the enemy comes</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22196C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22196C\"></sup>against the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Because they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22196D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22196D\"></sup>transgressed My covenantAnd rebelled against My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22196E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22196E\"></sup>law.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22197F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22197F\"></sup>They cry out to Me,“My God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22197G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22197G\"></sup>we of Israel know You!”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Israel has rejected the good;The enemy will pursue him.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22199H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22199H\"></sup>They have set up kings, but not by Me;They have appointed princes, but I did not know <i>it</i>.With their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22199I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22199I\"></sup>silver and gold they have made idols for themselves,That they might be cut off.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He has rejected your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22200J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22200J\"></sup>calf, O Samaria, <i>saying</i>,“My anger burns against them!”How long will they be incapable of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22200K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22200K\"></sup>innocence?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For from Israel is even this!A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22201L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22201L\"></sup>craftsman made it, so it is not God;Surely the calf of Samaria will be broken to pieces.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22202M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22202M\"></sup>they sow the windAnd they reap the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22202N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22202N\"></sup>whirlwind.The standing grain has no heads;It yields <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22202O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22202O\"></sup>no grain.Should it yield, strangers would swallow it up.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Israel is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22203P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22203P\"></sup>swallowed up;They are now among the nationsLike a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22203Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22203Q\"></sup>vessel in which no one delights.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For they have gone up to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22204R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22204R\"></sup>Assyria,<i>Like</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22204S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22204S\"></sup>a wild donkey all alone;Ephraim has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22204T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22204T\"></sup>hired lovers.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Even though they hire <i>allies</i> among the nations,Now I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22205U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22205U\"></sup>gather them up;And they will begin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22205V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22205V\"></sup>to diminishBecause of the burden of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22205W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22205W\"></sup>king of princes.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Since Ephraim has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22206X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22206X\"></sup>multiplied altars for sin,They have become altars of sinning for him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22207Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22207Y\"></sup>I wrote for him ten thousand <i>precepts</i> of My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22207Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22207Z\"></sup>law,They are regarded as a strange thing.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>As for My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22208AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22208AA\"></sup>sacrificial gifts,They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22208AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22208AB\"></sup>sacrifice the flesh and eat <i>it</i>,<i>But</i> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has taken no delight in them.Now He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22208AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22208AC\"></sup>remember their iniquity,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22208AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22208AD\"></sup>punish <i>them</i> for their sins;They will return to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22208AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22208AE\"></sup>Egypt.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For Israel has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22209AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22209AF\"></sup>forgotten his Maker and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22209AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22209AG\"></sup>built palaces;And Judah has multiplied fortified cities,But I will send a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22209AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22209AH\"></sup>fire on its cities that it may consume its palatial dwellings."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22210A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22210A\"></sup>Do not rejoice, O Israel, with exultation like the nations!For you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22210B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22210B\"></sup>played the harlot, forsaking your God.You have loved <i>harlots</i>’ earnings on every threshing floor.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Threshing floor and wine press will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22211C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22211C\"></sup>not feed them,And the new wine will fail them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They will not remain in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22212D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22212D\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> land,But Ephraim will return to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22212E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22212E\"></sup>Egypt,And in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22212F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22212F\"></sup>Assyria they will eat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22212G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22212G\"></sup>unclean <i>food</i>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They will not pour out drink offerings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22213H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22213H\"></sup>wine to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22213I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22213I\"></sup>Their sacrifices will not please Him.<i>Their bread will</i> <i>be</i> like mourners’ bread;All who eat of it will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22213J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22213J\"></sup>defiled,For their bread will be for themselves <i>alone</i>;It will not enter the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22214K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22214K\"></sup>What will you do on the day of the appointed festivalAnd on the day of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22214L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22214L\"></sup>feast of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For behold, they will go because of destruction;Egypt will gather them up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22215M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22215M\"></sup>Memphis will bury them.Weeds will take over their treasures of silver;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22215N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22215N\"></sup>Thorns <i>will be</i> in their tents.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22216O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22216O\"></sup>punishment have come,The days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22216P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22216P\"></sup>retribution have come;Let Israel know <i>this</i>!The prophet is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22216Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22216Q\"></sup>fool,The inspired man is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22216R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22216R\"></sup>demented,Because of the grossness of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22216S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22216S\"></sup>iniquity,And <i>because</i> your hostility is <i>so</i> great.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Ephraim <i>was</i> a watchman with my God, a prophet;<i>Yet</i> the snare of a bird catcher is in all his ways,<i>And</i> there is <i>only</i> hostility in the house of his God.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They have gone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22218T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22218T\"></sup>deep in depravityAs in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22218U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22218U\"></sup>Gibeah;He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22218V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22218V\"></sup>remember their iniquity,He will punish their sins.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I found Israel like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22219W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22219W\"></sup>grapes in the wilderness;I saw your forefathers as the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22219X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22219X\"></sup>earliest fruit on the fig tree in its first <i>season</i>.<i>But</i> they came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22219Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22219Y\"></sup>Baal-peor and devoted themselves to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22219Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22219Z\"></sup>shame,And they became as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22219AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22219AA\"></sup>detestable as that which they loved.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>As for Ephraim, their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22220AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22220AB\"></sup>glory will fly away like a bird—No birth, no pregnancy and no conception!",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Though they bring up their children,Yet I will bereave them until not a man is left.Yes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22221AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22221AC\"></sup>woe to them indeed when I depart from them!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Ephraim, as I have seen,Is planted in a pleasant meadow like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22222AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22222AD\"></sup>Tyre;But Ephraim will bring out his children for slaughter.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Give them, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—what will You give?Give them a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22223AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22223AE\"></sup>miscarrying womb and dry breasts.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>All their evil is at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22224AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22224AF\"></sup>Gilgal;Indeed, I came to hate them there!Because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22224AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22224AG\"></sup>wickedness of their deedsI will drive them out of My house!I will love them no more;All their princes are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22224AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22224AH\"></sup>rebels.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22225AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22225AI\"></sup>Ephraim is stricken, their root is dried up,They will bear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22225AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22225AJ\"></sup>no fruit.Even though they bear children,I will slay the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22225AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22225AK\"></sup>precious ones of their womb.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>My God will cast them awayBecause they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22226AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22226AL\"></sup>not listened to Him;And they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22226AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22226AM\"></sup>wanderers among the nations."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Israel is a luxuriant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22227A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22227A\"></sup>vine;He produces fruit for himself.The more his fruit,The more altars he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22227B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22227B\"></sup>made;The richer his land,The better he made the <i>sacred</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22227C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22227C\"></sup>pillars.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Their heart is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22228D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22228D\"></sup>faithless;Now they must bear their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22228E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22228E\"></sup>guilt.The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22228F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22228F\"></sup>break down their altars<i>And</i> destroy their <i>sacred</i> pillars.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Surely now they will say, “We have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22229G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22229G\"></sup>no king,For we do not revere the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.As for the king, what can he do for us?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They speak <i>mere</i> words,With <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22230H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22230H\"></sup>worthless oaths they make covenants;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22230I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22230I\"></sup>judgment sprouts like poisonous weeds in the furrows of the field.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The inhabitants of Samaria will fearFor the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22231J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22231J\"></sup>calf of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22231K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22231K\"></sup>Beth-aven.Indeed, its people will mourn for it,And its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22231L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22231L\"></sup>idolatrous priests will cry out over it,Over its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22231M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22231M\"></sup>glory, since it has departed from it.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The thing itself will be carried to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22232N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22232N\"></sup>AssyriaAs tribute to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22232O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22232O\"></sup>King Jareb;Ephraim will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22232P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22232P\"></sup>seized with shameAnd Israel will be ashamed of its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22232Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22232Q\"></sup>own counsel.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Samaria will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22233R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22233R\"></sup>cut off <i>with</i> her kingLike a stick on the surface of the water.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Also the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22234S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22234S\"></sup>high places of Aven, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22234T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22234T\"></sup>sin of Israel, will be destroyed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22234U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22234U\"></sup>Thorn and thistle will grow on their altars;Then they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22234V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22234V\"></sup>say to the mountains,“Cover us!” And to the hills, “Fall on us!”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>From the days of Gibeah you have sinned, O Israel;There they stand!Will not the battle against the sons of iniquity overtake them in Gibeah?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When it is My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22236W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22236W\"></sup>desire, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22236X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22236X\"></sup>chastise them;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22236Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22236Y\"></sup>the peoples will be gathered against themWhen they are bound for their double guilt.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Ephraim is a trained <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22237Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22237Z\"></sup>heifer that loves to thresh,But I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22237AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22237AA\"></sup>come over her fair neck <i>with a yoke</i>;I will harness Ephraim,Judah will plow, Jacob will harrow for himself.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22238AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22238AB\"></sup>Sow with a view to righteousness,Reap in accordance with kindness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22238AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22238AC\"></sup>Break up your fallow ground,For it is time to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22238AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22238AD\"></sup>seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>Until He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22238AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22238AE\"></sup>comes to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22238AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22238AF\"></sup>rain righteousness on you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22239AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22239AG\"></sup>plowed wickedness, you have reaped injustice,You have eaten the fruit of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22239AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22239AH\"></sup>lies.Because you have trusted in your way, in your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22239AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22239AI\"></sup>numerous warriors,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore a tumult will arise among your people,And all your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22240AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22240AJ\"></sup>fortresses will be destroyed,As Shalman destroyed Beth-arbel on the day of battle,<i>When</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22240AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22240AK\"></sup>mothers were dashed in pieces with <i>their</i> children.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Thus it will be done to you at Bethel because of your great wickedness.At dawn the king of Israel will be completely cut off."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>When Israel <i>was</i> a youth I loved him,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22242A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22242A\"></sup>out of Egypt I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22242B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22242B\"></sup>called My son.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The more <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22243C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22243C\"></sup>they called them,The more they went from them;They kept <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22243D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22243D\"></sup>sacrificing to the BaalsAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22243E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22243E\"></sup>burning incense to idols.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Yet it is I who taught Ephraim to walk,I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22244F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22244F\"></sup>took them in My arms;But they did not know that I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22244G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22244G\"></sup>healed them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22245H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22245H\"></sup>led them with cords of a man, with bonds of love,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22245I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22245I\"></sup>I became to them as one who lifts the yoke from their jaws;And I bent down <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22245J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22245J\"></sup>fed them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They will not return to the land of Egypt;But Assyria—he will be their kingBecause they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22246K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22246K\"></sup>refused to return <i>to Me</i>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22247L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22247L\"></sup>sword will whirl against their cities,And will demolish their gate barsAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22247M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22247M\"></sup>consume <i>them</i> because of their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22247N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22247N\"></sup>counsels.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So My people are bent on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22248O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22248O\"></sup>turning from Me.Though they call them to <i>the One</i> on high,None at all exalts <i>Him</i>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22249P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22249P\"></sup>How can I give you up, O Ephraim?How can I surrender you, O Israel?How can I make you like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22249Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22249Q\"></sup>Admah?How can I treat you like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22249R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22249R\"></sup>Zeboiim?My heart is turned over within Me,All My compassions are kindled.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22250S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22250S\"></sup>not execute My fierce anger;I will not destroy Ephraim <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22250T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22250T\"></sup>again.For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22250U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22250U\"></sup>I am God and not man, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22250V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22250V\"></sup>Holy One in your midst,And I will not come in wrath.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22251W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22251W\"></sup>walk after the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22251X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22251X\"></sup>roar like a lion;Indeed He will roarAnd <i>His</i> sons will come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22251Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22251Y\"></sup>trembling from the west.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They will come trembling like birds from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22252Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22252Z\"></sup>EgyptAnd like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22252AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22252AA\"></sup>doves from the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22252AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22252AB\"></sup>Assyria;And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22252AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22252AC\"></sup>settle them in their houses, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Ephraim surrounds Me with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22253AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22253AD\"></sup>liesAnd the house of Israel with deceit;Judah is also unruly against God,Even against the Holy One who is faithful."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Ephraim feeds on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22254A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22254A\"></sup>wind,And pursues the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22254B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22254B\"></sup>east wind continually;He multiplies lies and violence.Moreover, he makes a covenant with Assyria,And oil is carried to Egypt.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> also has a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22255C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22255C\"></sup>dispute with Judah,And will punish Jacob <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22255D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22255D\"></sup>according to his ways;He will repay him according to his deeds.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>In the womb he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22256E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22256E\"></sup>took his brother by the heel,And in his maturity he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22256F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22256F\"></sup>contended with God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Yes, he wrestled with the angel and prevailed;He wept and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22257G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22257G\"></sup>sought His favor.He found Him at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22257H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22257H\"></sup>BethelAnd there He spoke with us,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Even the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of hosts,The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22258I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22258I\"></sup>name.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22259J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22259J\"></sup>return to your God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22259K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22259K\"></sup>Observe kindness and justice,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22259L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22259L\"></sup>wait for your God continually.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>A merchant, in whose hands are false <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22260M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22260M\"></sup>balances,He loves to oppress.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And Ephraim said, “Surely I have become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22261N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22261N\"></sup>rich,I have found wealth for myself;In all my labors they will find in me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22261O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22261O\"></sup>No iniquity, which <i>would be</i> sin.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But I <i>have been</i> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God since the land of Egypt;I will make you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22262P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22262P\"></sup>live in tents again,As in the days of the appointed festival.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I have also spoken to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22263Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22263Q\"></sup>prophets,And I gave numerous visions,And through the prophets I gave <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22263R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22263R\"></sup>parables.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Is there iniquity <i>in</i> Gilead?Surely they are worthless.In Gilgal they sacrifice bulls,Yes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22264S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22264S\"></sup>their altars are like the stone heapsBeside the furrows of the field.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22265T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22265T\"></sup>Jacob fled to the land of Aram,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22265U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22265U\"></sup>Israel worked for a wife,And for a wife he kept <i>sheep</i>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But by a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22266V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22266V\"></sup>prophet the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> brought Israel from Egypt,And by a prophet he was kept.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22267W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22267W\"></sup>Ephraim has provoked to bitter anger;So his Lord will leave his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22267X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22267X\"></sup>bloodguilt on himAnd bring back his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22267Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22267Y\"></sup>reproach to him."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22268A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22268A\"></sup>When Ephraim spoke, <i>there was</i> trembling.He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22268B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22268B\"></sup>exalted himself in Israel,But through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22268C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22268C\"></sup>Baal he did wrong and died.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And now they sin more and more,And make for themselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22269D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22269D\"></sup>molten images,Idols <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22269E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22269E\"></sup>skillfully made from their silver,All of them the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22269F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22269F\"></sup>work of craftsmen.They say of them, “Let the men who sacrifice kiss the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22269G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22269G\"></sup>calves!”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore they will be like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22270H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22270H\"></sup>morning cloudAnd like dew which soon disappears,Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22270I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22270I\"></sup>chaff which is blown away from the threshing floorAnd like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22270J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22270J\"></sup>smoke from a chimney.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Yet I <i>have been</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22271K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22271K\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your GodSince the land of Egypt;And you were not to know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22271L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22271L\"></sup>any god except Me,For there is no savior <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22271M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22271M\"></sup>besides Me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22272N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22272N\"></sup>cared for you in the wilderness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22272O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22272O\"></sup>In the land of drought.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>As <i>they had</i> their pasture, they became <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22273P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22273P\"></sup>satisfied,And being satisfied, their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22273Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22273Q\"></sup>heart became proud;Therefore they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22273R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22273R\"></sup>forgot Me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So I will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22274S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22274S\"></sup>like a lion to them;Like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22274T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22274T\"></sup>leopard I will lie in wait by the wayside.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will encounter them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22275U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22275U\"></sup>like a bear robbed of her cubs,And I will tear open their chests;There I will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22275V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22275V\"></sup>devour them like a lioness,<i>As</i> a wild beast would tear them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><i>It is</i> your destruction, O Israel,That <i>you are</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22276W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22276W\"></sup>against Me, against your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22276X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22276X\"></sup>help.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Where now is your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22277Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22277Y\"></sup>kingThat he may save you in all your cities,And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22277Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22277Z\"></sup>judges of whom you requested,“Give me a king and princes”?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22278AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22278AA\"></sup>gave you a king in My angerAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22278AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22278AB\"></sup>took him away in My wrath.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The iniquity of Ephraim is bound up;His sin is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22279AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22279AC\"></sup>stored up.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The pains of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22280AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22280AD\"></sup>childbirth come upon him;He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22280AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22280AE\"></sup>not a wise son,For it is not the time that he should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22280AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22280AF\"></sup>delay at the opening of the womb.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Shall I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22281AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22281AG\"></sup>ransom them from the power of Sheol?Shall I redeem them from death?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22281AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22281AH\"></sup>O Death, where are your thorns?O Sheol, where is your sting?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22281AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22281AI\"></sup>Compassion will be hidden from My sight.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Though he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22282AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22282AJ\"></sup>flourishes among the reeds,An <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22282AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22282AK\"></sup>east wind will come,The wind of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> coming up from the wilderness;And his fountain will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22282AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22282AL\"></sup>become dryAnd his spring will be dried up;It will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22282AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22282AM\"></sup>plunder <i>his</i> treasury of every precious article.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Samaria will be held <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22283AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22283AN\"></sup>guilty,For she has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22283AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22283AO\"></sup>rebelled against her God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22283AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22283AP\"></sup>They will fall by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22283AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22283AQ\"></sup>sword,Their little ones will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22283AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22283AR\"></sup>dashed in pieces,And their pregnant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22283AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22283AS\"></sup>women will be ripped open."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22284A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22284A\"></sup>Return, O Israel, to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,For you have stumbled because of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22284B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22284B\"></sup>iniquity.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Take words with you and return to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.Say to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22285C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22285C\"></sup>Take away all iniquityAnd receive <i>us</i> graciously,That we may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22285D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22285D\"></sup>present the fruit of our lips.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Assyria will not save us,We will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22286E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22286E\"></sup>not ride on horses;Nor will we say again, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22286F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22286F\"></sup>Our god,’To the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22286G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22286G\"></sup>work of our hands;For in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22286H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22286H\"></sup>You the orphan finds mercy.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22287I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22287I\"></sup>heal their apostasy,I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22287J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22287J\"></sup>love them freely,For My anger has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22287K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22287K\"></sup>turned away from them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will be like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22288L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22288L\"></sup>dew to Israel;He will blossom like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22288M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22288M\"></sup>lily,And he will take root like <i>the cedars of</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22288N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22288N\"></sup>Lebanon.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>His shoots will sprout,And his beauty will be like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22289O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22289O\"></sup>olive treeAnd his fragrance like <i>the cedars of</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22289P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22289P\"></sup>Lebanon.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22290Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22290Q\"></sup>live in his shadowWill again raise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22290R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22290R\"></sup>grain,And they will blossom like the vine.His renown <i>will be</i> like the wine of Lebanon.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>O Ephraim, what more have I to do with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22291S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22291S\"></sup>idols?It is I who answer and look after you.I am like a luxuriant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22291T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22291T\"></sup>cypress;From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22291U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22291U\"></sup>Me comes your fruit.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22292V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22292V\"></sup>Whoever is wise, let him understand these things;<i>Whoever</i> is discerning, let him know them.For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22292W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22292W\"></sup>ways of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> are right,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22292X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22292X\"></sup>righteous will walk in them,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-22292Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-22292Y\"></sup>transgressors will stumble in them."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;